            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[区块链]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy S25]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286566</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">距离三星 Galaxy Unpacked 发布会越来越近，有关 Galaxy S25 系列新机的消息亦越来越多。近日，外媒 Android Headlines 独家曝光了多张 Galaxy S25 系列官方渲染图，完整揭露了 S25、S25+和 S25 Ultra 三款新机的外观设计及配色。与此同时，更详细的规格信息亦被披露</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br /></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">。</span></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">设计革新</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">相比上一代产品，新系列最显著的设计变化出现在 Galaxy S25 Ultra 上，其边角设计变得更为圆润。三款机型均采用平面屏幕、平面机背及直边框设计，边框在边缘处略有弧度。值得注意的是，相机模组设计也有所改良，采用上宽下窄的设计，灵感源自传统相机镜头桶的外观。</span></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">多彩配色方案</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">三星为不同机型提供了独特的配色选择：</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 及 S25+提供冰蓝色、薄荷绿、海军蓝和银影色四种选择</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 Ultra 则主打高端质感，推出钛黑色、钛灰色、钛银蓝色及钛白银色四款配色</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">硬件规格升级</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">根据已曝光的规格信息，S25 系列三款新机均搭载高通骁龙 8 Elite for Galaxy 处理器，预计是骁龙 8 Elite 的超频版本，性能表现值得期待。此外，三款新机均配备 12GB RAM，而 S25 Ultra 在部分市场更可能提供 16GB RAM 版本。系统方面，S25 系列将预载基于 Android 15 的 One UI 7 客制化介面，并支持 Wi-Fi 7 和蓝牙 5.3 等最新无线技术。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 Ultra 规格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.9 吋 WQHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">120Hz 自适应刷新率</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">5000mAh 大容量电池，支援 45W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">后置四镜头系统：200MP 主摄 + 50MP 超广角 + 10MP 长焦 (3 倍光学变焦) + 50MP 潜望式长焦 (5 倍光学变焦)</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25+规格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.7 吋 WQHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">4900mAh 电池，支援 45W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">后置三镜头系统，配置与标准版相同</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 规格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.2 吋 FHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">4000mAh 电池，支援 25W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">后置 50MP 主摄 + 12MP 超广角 + 10MP 长焦三镜头系统</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">三星预计在 1 月 22 日的 Galaxy Unpacked 发布会上正式发布新机系列。除了展示硬件规格外，市场预期三星还将重点介绍新一代 AI 智能功能。有传闻指出可能会同场预告 Galaxy S25 Slim 版本，但细节仍未确定。</span></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.androidheadlines.com/samsung-galaxy-s25-series-design" target="_blank" rel="noopener">androidheadlines</a></p><br /><b>
