        <item>
            <title>优化车辆牌照系统运作良好，运输署称保障车主私隐及便利性</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/13/td-enhanced-renew-licence/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=td-enhanced-renew-licence</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/13/td-enhanced-renew-licence/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 01:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[牌费]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[车牌]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[车辆牌照]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运输署]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286548</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>运输署自 2024 年 12 月 30 日推出优化车辆牌照续领措施后，运作顺畅。署方表示，执法人员现时利用特定流动应用程式，能即时查阅车辆牌照的最新届满日期，避免因查询平台资料延迟更新而影响执法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/90c5f330d303ccaf3108-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/90c5f330d303ccaf3108-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/90c5f330d303ccaf3108.jpg 1081w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>运输署亦已向成功续领行车证的车主发出通知书，明确列出最新牌照有效期。此外，署方提供一个网上平台，车主可透过该平台查询牌照届满日期。然而，为保障车主的个人资料，车主需输入「登记为车主日期」后，才可查阅相关资讯。署方强调，已与警方保持紧密联系，并密切观察措施的实施情况，确保措施运行稳定，并继续提供车主便利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/td-694x401.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="401" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/td-694x401.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/td-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源: <a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1787114-20250111.htm?spTabChangeable=0">rthk</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
